<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8"/>
<title>Marker BARCODE 2 — Chaource AOP</title>
<style>
  @page { size: A4; margin: 0; }
  * { margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; }
  body { width:210mm; height:297mm; display:flex; flex-direction:column; align-items:center; justify-content:center; background:white; font-family: Georgia, serif; }
  .page { width:180mm; display:flex; flex-direction:column; align-items:center; gap:10mm; }
  .title { font-size:18pt; color:#8b5e00; letter-spacing:0.1em; text-align:center; }
  .subtitle { font-size:10pt; color:#666; text-align:center; margin-top:-6mm; }
  .marker-wrap { border: 4mm solid black; padding:5mm; background:white; }
  svg { display:block; }
  .instructions { font-size:9pt; color:#555; text-align:center; line-height:1.8; border-top:1px solid #ddd; padding-top:6mm; width:100%; }
  .instructions strong { color:#8b5e00; }
  .badge { background:#8b5e00; color:white; font-size:8pt; letter-spacing:0.2em; padding:2mm 6mm; text-transform:uppercase; margin-top:4mm; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="page">
  <div class="title">🧀 CHAOURCE AOP</div>
  <div class="subtitle">Marker AR — Inquadra con la fotocamera</div>

  <!--
    BARCODE 3x3 value=2 per AR.js
    Valore 2 binario: 000 / 000 / 010  → cella (1,2) nera
  -->
  <div class="marker-wrap">
    <svg width="120mm" height="120mm" viewBox="0 0 700 700" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
      <rect width="700" height="700" fill="white"/>
      <rect x="0" y="0" width="700" height="700" fill="black"/>
      <rect x="100" y="100" width="500" height="500" fill="white"/>

      <!-- Cella 1,2 = bit1 = 1 → NERA -->
      <rect x="300" y="400" width="100" height="100" fill="black"/>

      <!-- Quadrati di orientamento -->
      <!-- Alto-sinistra -->
      <rect x="120" y="120" width="140" height="140" fill="black"/>
      <rect x="140" y="140" width="100" height="100" fill="white"/>
      <rect x="160" y="160" width="60"  height="60"  fill="black"/>
      <!-- Alto-destra -->
      <rect x="440" y="120" width="140" height="140" fill="black"/>
      <rect x="460" y="140" width="100" height="100" fill="white"/>
      <rect x="480" y="160" width="60"  height="60"  fill="black"/>
      <!-- Basso-sinistra -->
      <rect x="120" y="440" width="140" height="140" fill="black"/>
      <rect x="140" y="460" width="100" height="100" fill="white"/>
      <rect x="160" y="480" width="60"  height="60"  fill="black"/>

      <!-- Icona centrale -->
      <text x="310" y="320" font-size="100" text-anchor="middle" dominant-baseline="middle">🧀</text>
    </svg>
  </div>

  <div class="badge">MARKER 3 — BARCODE 2</div>

  <div class="instructions">
    <strong>Come usare questo marker:</strong><br>
    1. Stampa questa pagina in bianco e nero su carta A4<br>
    2. Apri la Camera AR sul tuo smartphone<br>
    3. Tieni il foglio su un piano orizzontale con buona illuminazione<br>
    4. Punta la fotocamera a 20–40 cm dal marker<br>
    5. Apparirà il formaggio Chaource 3D con i dati di produzione
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
